USipho Mbatha ugwetshwe yinkantolo yaseMtshezi ngoLwesihlanu emuva kokulahlwa ngamacala amabili okubulala. Ngokobufakazi obuphambi kwenkantolo ngo-Meyi 5, 2018, phakathi kwamabili uMnuz Xolani Ngcobo (34), wayeshayela eWembezi ehamba nomngani wakhe uMnuz Sbonelo Madlala (23) ngesikhathi kudlula umuntu owayengaziwa eduze kwemoto yabo wavulela ngenhlamvu, ebhekise kubona. Izinhlambu zibathole kaningana emzimbeni bashonela khona lapho. Amaphoyisa aseWembezi avula amacala amabili okubulala. Kwaba nophenyo abaphenyi bagcina bebophe indoda eWembezi. Kwavela ukuthi umbulali, wayekade exabane noyedwa kubafi. Umbulali waphucwa isibhamu sahanjiswa sayohlolwa kwavela ukuthi yisona esasetshenziswa ukubulala abafi. Ubelokhu ehamba icala waze wagcina egwetshiwe.  